    <item>
      <title>随着加拿大经济疲软，丰业银行贷款损失准备金上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/scotiabank-loan-loss-provisions-rise-as-canadian-economy-weakens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于加拿大经济疲软以及拉美业务零售借款人拖欠率上升，消费者贷款压力日益加大，新斯科舍银行的贷款损失准备金未达到分析师的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/scotiabank-loan-loss-provisions-rise-as-canadian-economy-weakens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:47:24 GMT</pubDate>
